58
00:03:59.906 --> 00:04:02.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
早くおいしいものを食べたい
という一心が―

59
00:04:02.784 --> 00:04:05.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
回復を早めるということも
あるんじゃないですか

60
00:04:05.828 --> 00:04:09.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
えらいまあ 人ごとや思うて
ええ加減なことを

61
00:04:09.582 --> 00:04:10.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そや 山岡はん

62
00:04:11.209 --> 00:04:12.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
わしが退院したら―

63
00:04:12.585 --> 00:04:15.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
