約束しとくんなはれ

64
00:04:15.630 --> 00:04:16.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
えっ

65
00:04:17.048 --> 00:04:18.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それを楽しみにしとったら

66
00:04:18.758 --> 00:04:21.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
