67
00:04:22.011 --> 00:04:23.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ふーん

68
00:04:24.180 --> 00:04:25.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
山岡くん

69
00:04:25.139 --> 00:04:27.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
僕からもお願いするよ
引き受けてくれ

70
00:04:27.350 --> 00:04:29.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
