76
00:04:39.737 --> 00:04:41.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
はいはい
ごちそうして差し上げましょう

77
00:04:42.365 --> 00:04:45.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
