そやなあ うーん

81
00:04:51.124 --> 00:04:53.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
今 目に浮かぶのは…

82
00:04:54.335 --> 00:04:58.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
天ぷらや
それも鮎の天ぷらや

83
00:04:58.881 --> 00:05:00.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
鮎の天ぷら？

84
00:05:01.134 --> 00:05:02.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京極）そや 鮎天や

85
00:05:03.928 --> 00:05:05.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
鮎天はええでえ

