00:05:06.180 --> 00:05:09.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
さっくりと骨まで歯が通って
身はホロホロして―

87
00:05:09.684 --> 00:05:12.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
甘く上品な苦さのはらわたの
あの香ばしさ

88
00:05:13.479 --> 00:05:15.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああ
鮎を天ぷらにするんですか

89
00:05:15.815 --> 00:05:17.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
聞いただけでおいしそうですね

90
00:05:17.567 --> 00:05:21.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああ 天ぷらのタネの中では
やはり鮎が最高や

91
00:05:22.447 --> 00:05:23.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
分かりました

92
00:05:23.614 --> 00:05:26.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
京極さんのお気に召すような
鮎の天ぷらを

93
00:05:26.284 --> 00:05:27.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
きっと作って差し上げますよ

94
00:05:28.077 --> 00:05:28.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おおきに

95
00:05:29.037 --> 00:05:32.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
山岡はんならきっと最高の鮎天を
食べさせてくれるやろ

96
00:05:32.999 --> 00:05:34.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それ楽しみにしとったら

97
00:05:34.459 --> 00:05:37.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
治りが早うなること
間違いなしや ハハハ

98
00:05:38.171 --> 00:05:40.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（足音）

99
00:05:40.381 --> 00:05:44.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
