100
00:05:44.427 --> 00:05:45.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
感謝しますで

101
00:05:45.553 --> 00:05:48.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これがホントのケガの功名だな
富井くん

102
00:05:48.431 --> 00:05:50.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（足音）

103
00:05:51.684 --> 00:05:54.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
