私たちはそろそろ

104
00:05:56.647 --> 00:05:57.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
はい　どうぞ

105
00:06:02.195 --> 00:06:03.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
