106
00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（海原雄山）また目障りな

107
00:06:08.576 --> 00:06:09.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
なに？

108
00:06:10.244 --> 00:06:12.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いやいや これは海原先生

109
00:06:12.371 --> 00:06:14.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
わざわざお越しくださるとは
恐縮ですな

110
00:06:18.336 --> 00:06:21.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（海原）いやあ
とんだご災難でしたな 京極さん

111
00:06:21.631 --> 00:06:25.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
しかし 捻挫(ねんざ)だけで済むとは
不幸中の幸い

112
00:06:25.176 --> 00:06:27.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
むしろいい休養になるじゃ
ありませんか

113
00:06:27.470 --> 00:06:28.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ハハハハ

114
00:06:28.679 --> 00:06:32.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
今も私の悪運の強さを
自慢しとったとこですわ

115
00:06:32.892 --> 00:06:36.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
まっ それにしても早く元気に
なっていただかんとな

116
00:06:36.479 --> 00:06:40.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
退院されたらお祝いに何か
ごちそうして差し上げましょう

117
00:06:40.399 --> 00:06:42.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え… いやあ

118
00:06:42.318 --> 00:06:43.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そのことやったら

119
00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:46.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
実は山岡はんがわしに―

120
00:06:46.697 --> 00:06:48.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ごちそうしてくれることに
なってましてな

121
00:06:49.117 --> 00:06:51.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
士郎が京極さんに

122
00:06:51.452 --> 00:06:54.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
