123
00:06:54.664 --> 00:06:57.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それも鮎の天ぷらですわ

124
00:06:57.208 --> 00:06:59.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この年まで鮎をさんざん
食べ尽くしてくると

125
00:06:59.961 --> 00:07:03.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
