鮎天で食べとうなったりしましてな

126
00:07:03.756 --> 00:07:04.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
なるほど

127
00:07:04.799 --> 00:07:07.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
